</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_209" id="104r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_209_r1l19"><expan>Pet<ex>er</ex>man</expan> von Stet </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_209_r1l20"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex>man</expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Sebolt Schucʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_209_r1l21"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / Alſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir Jn <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> beſant / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_209_r1l22"><expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> brief hören laſſen / vnd er hat vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / Er hab </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_209_r1l23">vormals mit ew rechnen <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd ew becʒalt ſo <expan>v<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / daʒ 
<del rend="strikethrough">Jr </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_209_r1l24">er maint / Jr ſeit Jm ee ſchuldig <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> er ew / . 
<del rend="strikethrough">do ſo me </del> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_209_r1l25">als Jr <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan> Er ſüll <expan>and<ex>er</ex>weıt</expan> mit ew rechnen / 
<del rend="strikethrough">künn er a </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_209_r1l27">müg er alſpald <expan>nyema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> <expan>gehab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd er wöll <expan>hiecʒwıſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_209_r1l28"><expan>Pfingſt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>beſeh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd etwem empfelhen / der ew <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſache von </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_209_r1l26">rechnung </ab></add> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_209_r1l29">
<del rend="strikethrough">ſeinen <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan></del> erÿnnern ſülle / . ob Jr mit <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeinen <expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan> einig </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_209_r1l30"><expan>werd<ex>e</ex>n</expan> möcht / wer <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> daʒ Jr kein <expan>benüge<ex>n</ex></expan> daran hett / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_209_r1l31">hett Jr <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒü <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> icht cʒeſprechen <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_209_r1l32">
<del rend="strikethrough">ſo </del> wöllen vvir ew / <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>ſcheinbot<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> vollen gevvalt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_209_r1l33"><expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒogens</expan> ſlewnigs rechten <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> vor des Reichs <expan>Richt<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_209_r1l34">vvenn wir des ermant <expan>vverde<ex>n</ex></expan> / So derſelb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> anheim iſt / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_209_r1l35"><expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> <expan>S<ex>e</ex>c<ex>un</ex>da</expan> poſt Erhardj / Anno etc . xȷ<hi rend="sup">o</hi> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_209" id="104r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Pet<ex>er</ex>man</expan> von Stet </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex>man</expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Sebolt Schucz,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        also <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir in <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> besant und <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        brief hören lassen und er hat uns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, er hab
                        vormals mit ew rechnen <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> und ew beczalt so
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, daz er maint, ir seit im ee schuldig
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> er ew. Und als ir
                            <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan>, er süll
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex>weit</expan> mit ew rechnen, müg er alspald
                                <expan>nyema<ex>n</ex>t</expan>
<expan>gehab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, und er wöll
                            <expan>hieczwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                        <app><note><q type="date"><expan>pfingst<ex>e</ex>n</expan></q>31.05.1411</note></app>
<expan>beseh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und etwem empfelhen, der ew
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add>rechnung</add> erynnern sülle, ob ir mit <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> seinen <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> einig
                                <expan>werd<ex>e</ex>n</expan> möcht. Wer
                            <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>, daz ir kein
                            <expan>benüge<ex>n</ex></expan> daran hett, hett ir
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> czü <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> icht czesprechen,
                                <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> wöllen wir ew
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>scheinbot<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> vollen
                        gewalt <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czogens</expan> slewnigs rechten
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> vor des reichs
                            <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> czu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>,
                        wenn wir des ermant <expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan>, so derselb
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> anheim ist. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan>
<expan>s<ex>e</ex>c<ex>un</ex>da</expan> post Erhardi anno etc. xi<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
